data.description: Don't miss this super cute 3 bedroom / 2-bathroom home on an almost 1/4 acre lot and with a metal roof in popular Portland! This home includes a gourmet gas kitchen with a preparation island, upgraded stainless appliances, and lots of storage; the open living room includes a gas log fireplace; and the Primary Bathroom includes a large walk-in shower and massive walk-in closet. Enjoy entertaining and a cool beverage under the shade of the courtyard Pergola. By the way, are you worried about utility costs? This home was built with extra insulation that saves on energy bills. Also, no need to worry about rolling blackouts either! This home comes with a full-house generator that clicks on whenever the power goes off! If you need space for guest parking, this home has a spacious garage and also includes an extra-large driveway. Seller will provide allowance for new flooring. Schedule your showing today!
